{"tid":2438232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年被控管有雷射筆 警一秒判斷被告閃縮驚慌","createTime":"2021-03-08T11:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:20:58.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"789bda925ead872aa85a86032d24a88a6b0bab98","tid":2438232,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"前年聖誕節當天，網民發起<span class=\"red\">「和你shop」活動</span>，多區爆發警民衝突，多人被捕。當中16歲男生被指在<span class=\"red\">旺角藏有一支雷射筆</span>，他否認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，今在九龍城裁判法院受審。截停及拘捕被告的警員在盤問下同意，當晚旺角有很多途人，當中沒有人使用武力或雷射筆。警員又同意觀察被告的時間很短，僅有1至2秒，便認為被告眼神閃避及神情驚慌，繼而截停及搜查他。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出，被告遭截停前，曾經語帶<span class=\"red\">挑釁地向梁查詢</span>：「阿sir，前面行唔行得？點行過去呀？」梁回應「行你就行啦，你咁多嘢講」，並<span class=\"red\">因而截停被告搜身</span>。梁全部不同意，亦不同意憑直覺決定截停甚麼人。惟梁同意，被告遭截停後一度表明正返回深水埗住所途中，而且若非遭警方截停，被告向前繼續行，便很可能回到家。"},{"pid":"5e16fbb500999a59d4e84a41fd434a8af7b8302d","tid":2438232,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/YHPJR52EP5GWXOFLUQKBKDMS5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FYHPJR52EP5GWXOFLUQKBKDMS5Q%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=0aee2d4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FYHPJR52EP5GWXOFLUQKBKDMS5Q%2F&h=203595d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/YHPJR52EP5GWXOFLUQKBKDMS5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"45c42d2b0c619c19003a1c1fac7e9aa6bed3cb1b","tid":2438232,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5692bff0e096229b3096389a52013c92585194e9","tid":2438232,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0cd7b58165b31ba0c2b9ac8fffad2fa0a59313","tid":2438232,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}